> Built an autonomous multi-agent code review system using LangGraph with three specialized agents (static analysis, bug triage, fix suggestion), tool calling (Pylint, AST, Tavily Search), shared memory via LangGraph SqliteSaver checkpointer, and conditional routing with automatic second-pass for critical bugs — achieving **X% bug classification accuracy** on a 10-snippet eval set. Deployed via Streamlit.

